{"tid":674674,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"想請問食緊A酸可唔可以飲健身奶粉?","createTime":"2018-05-23T01:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T12:48:05.000Z","uid":64376,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5df17cb1333f4539dd39b9ac26a92f02b3f102e9","tid":674674,"uid":64376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:55:18.000Z","msg":"小弟岩岩開始食緊N牌A酸10日, 平時健身開, 不過因為工作關係食唔夠蛋白質所以想飲蛋白奶粉, 唔知有無朋友試過兩樣一齊食而無咩異樣? 我問過醫生佢就話應該無咩野 但臨尾又話食緊a酸唔好搞咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我真係食雞食到反胃...我知a酸會令皮膚乾燥 奶粉亦會令身體熱氣 所以我打算2個鐘就飲水 希望無咁大影響。 唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470ac259a3bc1b6355bacad6d3c06d9544397e32","tid":674674,"uid":184247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T02:01:38.000Z","msg":"最好唔好，本身A酸會改變你體質，會對肝同骨有負擔，食大隻奶粉怕你增生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd4ac960f768a71e9f280dee4c5571045da9c02","tid":674674,"uid":64376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"470ac259a3bc1b6355bacad6d3c06d9544397e32","tid":674674,"uid":184247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T02:01:38.000Z","msg":"最好唔好，本身A酸會改變你體質，會對肝同骨有負擔，食大隻奶粉怕你增生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"唔該你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但如果我飲多啲水呢 ?"},{"pid":"354e0a3089bc49dfd220872ff1a57c455985a6e4","tid":674674,"uid":64376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3d7a5b3989dfe560f472a586c18e5f80d78297","tid":674674,"uid":50926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:51:22.000Z","msg":"健身奶粉只不過係蛋白質"},{"pid":"8d2128dfd8c96fb1b945cfd5494958980b2b31cd","tid":674674,"uid":64376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f3d7a5b3989dfe560f472a